No. 10-5297. Johnny Begay, Petitioner v. United States. 562 U.S. 954, 131 S. Ct. 272,

178 L. Ed. 2d 252,

2010 U.S. LEXIS 7700. October 4, 2010.

Petition for writ of certiorari to the United States Court of Appeals for the Tenth Circuit denied.

Same case below, 602 F.3d 1150.
